dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Bemand\"}, {\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Six_Nations_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9999999987080628, \"rank\": 1.291646948324807e-09, \"text\": \"Six Nations\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Six_Nations_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Six_Nations_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"B\\u00e9ibhinn Parsons, Eve Higgins, Aoibheann Reilly and Katie Heffernan, an unused substitute on Saturday, are among those who have crossed over between the codes.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 354, \"end\": 362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B\\u00e9\\u1e03inn\", \"score\": 0.934115051658946, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"B\\u00e9ibhinn\", \"types\": [\"Q82799\", \"Q202444\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B\\u00e9\\u1e03inn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B\\u00e9\\u1e03inn\"}, {\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Parsons\", \"score\": 0.9997716631359077, \"rank\": 0.00022838749869397273, \"text\": \"Parsons\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Parsons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Parsons\"}, {\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve_Higgins\", \"score\": 0.9999861426777606, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eve Higgins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve_Higgins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve_Higgins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are two more World Series events, in Singapore and Madrid next month, before the Paris Games in July and Bemand told RT\\u00c9 Sport that he has held discussions with Ireland sevens head coach Allan Temple-Jones about his squad selection.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8562502851490936, \"rank\": 0.16347918523744112, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"score\": 0.9997509100978217, \"rank\": 0.00024915028034908375, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\"}, {\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999789533833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 682, \"end\": 689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998669045542, \"rank\": 1.3302837491804499e-07, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Players like winger Corrigan, who scored three tries in her first Six Nations, and back row Aoife Wafer, Ireland's player of the tournament, could come into the equation.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998669045542, \"rank\": 1.3302837491804499e-07, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Absolutely.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to represent Irish rugby to the highest possible standard that we can,\\\" said the 45-year-old.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9996439700990793, \"rank\": 0.0003558664405557522, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The great work that Katie has been doing absolutely there is discussions being had and Katie will get an opportunity to put her hand up for an Olympics.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Myself and TJ [Allan Temple-Jones] have had continued and good conversations around players.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's up to him (TJ) in terms of his selections and where it goes from there but players are available.\\\"\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about her experience with sevens and a possible shot at becoming an Olympian, 20-year-old Corrigan (above) said: \\\"I did underage Sevens and I went to Marcoussis in France a few times and yeah, I like the Sevens but playing now, you got a taste of the 15s and I love that as well.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1475, \"end\": 1483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999994850274068, \"rank\": 5.149730561145879e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999982605914, \"rank\": 1.7337286734909413e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, I do not know.\\\"\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, one player who has ruled herself out of contention is Brittany Hogan, player of the match in the 15-12 win over the Scots.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miss_California_USA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brittany Hogan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miss_California_USA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miss_California_USA\"}, {\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"score\": 0.9334327332736736, \"rank\": 0.07047371652045549, \"text\": \"Scots\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was involved in the Sevens squad a few years ago,\\\" Hogan (below) said.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I am a little bit too slow for that now.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had to pack on a good bit of kgs, muscle-wise for the back row so we will see how it goes but I do not really think that's on the cards for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the Ireland 15s will take a break before a summer camp ahead of WXV1 in Canada.\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2206, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999222382, \"rank\": 7.022161568313698e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will face England, France and one of Australia, Canada, New Zealand and USA in September and October.\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2230, \"end\": 2237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.999996581660911, \"rank\": 3.4182397869259945e-06, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2239, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999982605914, \"rank\": 1.7337286734909413e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2257, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999991464392, \"rank\": 8.535118565741766e-10, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2268, \"end\": 2274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999222382, \"rank\": 7.022161568313698e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2276, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999643483891093, \"rank\": 3.565278400790513e-05, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999995939106, \"rank\": 2.71803053168271e-10, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After finishing last season pointless, they secured two wins against Wales and Scotland, and a losing bonus point against Italy in Bemand's first year in charge.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2392, \"end\": 2397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999305846383, \"rank\": 4.250766589971487e-08, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2402, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999908141, \"rank\": 6.613540752838869e-11, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.529579077804167e-11, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He admits there is plenty of work to be done in order to compete with the likes of the Red Roses, who wrapped up a fifth successive Grand Slam whenbeating France on Saturday.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"score\": 0.9999963365411334, \"rank\": 3.663472449525379e-06, \"text\": \"Slam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\"}, {\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999982605914, \"rank\": 1.7337286734909413e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Set-piece is massive in northern hemisphere teams,\\\" said the former Bath and Harlequins scrum-half (above) when asked what areas for improvement he will focus on.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need to be able to handle the ball and stress and stretch teams.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We need to be able to kick the ball.\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, we have got some good kickers.\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We need to just develop that side of the game a little bit in terms of variety and where and how you get material advantage from it.\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 3111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have really had barely any time, we are only just getting started into it so we have got plenty to go at...and it's a great opportunity for us.\\\"\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch highlights of the weekend's rugby action on Against the Head, 8pm, RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player  Follow theRT\\u00c9 Sport WhatsApp channelfor the best news, interviews, analysis and features, as well as details of our sports coverage across all RT\\u00c9 platforms      \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3336, \"end\": 3340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"score\": 0.9994238889060038, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c92\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\"}, {\"begin\": 3345, \"end\": 3348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 3377, \"end\": 3385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999997699196947, \"rank\": 2.3008018467142418e-07, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}, {\"begin\": 3500, \"end\": 3503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's N